OPTOMA CORP (3565)  said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 0.50% to NT$441,153,000 from NT$443,368,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            441,153          443,368    
YOY%              -0.50%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,789,074        1,658,980   
YOY%              7.84%  
=================================================================
 